Package: causalSenseCheck
Title: Causal Robustness Stress Tests for Applied Research
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Ruiyi", "Yang", , "yryrena@gmail.com", role = c("aut","cre"))
Description: Quick, standardized stress tests for causal claims, including
    sensitivity to unobserved confounding, placebo checks, and cross-estimator
    comparisons (OLS, DR/AIPW, IV, DID, GRF).
